## Commands — Frame Save Karne Ke Liye

**Step 1 — Environment source karo (har naye terminal mein):**
```bash
source ~/.bashrc
source ~/Desktop/SDV_workspace/install/setup.bash
```

**Step 2 — RealSense camera start karo (Terminal 1):**
```bash
ros2 run qcar2_nodes rgbd
```

**Step 3 — Raw frame save karo (Terminal 2):**
```bash
python3 ~/Desktop/SDV_workspace/scripts/save_frame.py
```

**Step 4 — Perception node launch karo (Terminal 2):**
```bash
ros2 launch sdv_perception perception_launch.py
```

**Step 5 — Annotated frame save karo (Terminal 3):**
```bash
python3 ~/Desktop/SDV_workspace/scripts/save_annotated.py
```

**Step 6 — Files kahan hain:**
```
Raw frames:       ~/Desktop/SDV_workspace/scripts/frame_1.jpg
Annotated frames: ~/Desktop/SDV_workspace/scripts/annotated_1.jpg
ROI image:        ~/Desktop/SDV_workspace/scripts/roi.jpg
Bird's eye:       ~/Desktop/SDV_workspace/scripts/birdseye.jpg
```

